        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks FCD for information.</p> 
<p>Hopes that translation of his paper will appear in <hi rend="italic">Dublin Journal</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Notes experience of his son [Leonard Darwin] on engorgement of eyes with blood. Discusses secretion of tears when eye muscles are involuntarily contracted.</p>
        </abstract>
